styleUrlsData.data:
#title
    background-color: #fff
    position: absolute
    z-index: 10
    margin: 1vh 1vh
    padding: 3vh 3vh

components.name: InspectorComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
#container
    margin: 1%
    padding: 2% 1% 0 1%
    border: #000 solid 1px

mat-form-field
    width: 100%

.readonly-property
    border-left: medium solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)
    margin: 0 0 2em 0
    padding: 1em 0 1em 0

.readonly-property p
    margin: 0 0 0 1em
    font-size: 16px

.readonly-property p > span
    font-weight: bold

.readonly
    display: none

components.templateData:
Requirement

URL: {{ url ? url.href : '#' }}

components.name: OrgChartComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
#app-org-chart
    background: whitesmoke
    width: 75vw
    height: 98vh
    border: 1px solid black
    margin-right: 0
    margin-left: auto
    margin-top: 0

#app-minimap
    position: absolute
    margin: 32px
    top: 0
    right: 0
    width: 16%
    height: 16%
    border: 1px solid black
    z-index: 5
